parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor
the brakes need to be pumped multiple times to stop the vehicle
the brake pedal has a spongy or soft feel
the brakes produce a burning smell
smoke is visible from the wheels
the low brake pressure light illuminates.
